window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I'm the key to an ancient power. And my mate will kill anyone who dares to touch me.</p> <p>I never asked to be the key to an ancient power, but here I amâ€”trapped by a ruthless wolf enforcer who thinks he can control me. Big mistake. Because Angelo, my fated mate and the most dangerous mafia king in New Orleans, is tearing the city apart to find me. And he doesn't believe in mercy.</p> <p>As if being caught in a supernatural tug-of-war wasn't enough, now I'm at the center of a violent clash between rival mafia families. Every second I'm held captive, Angelo's rage grows darker, deadlier. His message is clear: touch his mate, forfeit your life.</p> <p>With my best friend's life hanging in the balance and a cunning demon whispering tempting offers, the stakes keep rising. My growing powers might be our only hope, but they're as unpredictable as Angelo's wrath. Time is running out, and my captors are about to learn why you never steal from the French Quarter's most lethal vampire king.</p> <p>One thing is certain: New Orleans will run red before Angelo lets anyone keep me from him.</p> <p><i>The Curse of Blood and Silence</i> is the second book in the French Quarter Vampire King series. This steamy vampire mafia romance features a possessive mate, deadly consequences, forced proximity, forbidden passion, and dark supernatural thrills that will keep you listening all night!</p>"; 
